OL,3,CMan found guilty of murdering
OL,4,Chousemate over #10 phone debt
OL,6,FA Kent man who stabbed his housemate
OL,7,Fbecause of an argument over a #10
OL,8,Fphone debt has been found guilty of
OL,9,Fhis murder.
OL,11,FMark Jesse attacked Charles Belsham at
OL,12,Ftheir shared home in Castle Road,
OL,13,FChatham, last November.
OL,15,FThe 51 year old was convicted
OL,16,Ffollowing a trial at Maidstone Crown
OL,17,FCourt.
OL,19,FHe will be sentenced at a later date.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/5
