OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1781687892
OL,3,CMan found guilty of murdering
OL,4,Chousemate over #10 phone debt
OL,6,FMr Belsham had been arguing with a
OL,7,Fvisitor, Ashley Robinson, at the time
OL,8,Fof the incident, a court heard.
OL,10,FIt concerned a phone which the victim
OL,11,Fhad allegedly not paid Robinson #10
OL,12,Ffor.
OL,14,FJesse became angered by the argument,
OL,15,Fpicked up a knife and entered Mr
OL,16,FBelsham's room with another man,
OL,17,Fprosecutors said.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
