OL,3,CMan found guilty of murdering
OL,4,Chousemate over #10 phone debt
OL,6,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FHe then attacked the victim and left
OL,12,Fthe room, where Jesse was reported to
OL,13,Fhave said "I've stabbed him in the
OL,14,Fribs".
OL,16,FEmergency services later attended the
OL,17,Fproperty, where Mr Belsham was found
OL,18,Fwith a single, fatal stab wound to the
OL,19,Fchest.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/5
