CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1781687892
OL,3,CMan found guilty of murdering
OL,4,Chousemate over #10 phone debt
OL,6,FJesse and Robinson fled the house
OL,7,Ftogether and drove away before
OL,8,Fabandoning their car. They were both
OL,9,Farrested over the next two days.
OL,11,FRobinson was also convicted of
OL,12,Fassisting an offender.
OL,14,FKent Police Detective Chief Inspector
OL,15,FMartin Davies said Mr Belsham died
OL,16,Fbecause of Jesse's "unjustifiable and
OL,17,Frash decision" to attack him.
OL,19,FHe added: "That he ran from the scene
OL,20,Fand consistently denied his actions
OL,21,Fshow his lack of remorse and morality.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/5
