OL,3,CMan found guilty of murdering
OL,4,Chousemate over #10 phone debt
OL,6,F"There is no more serious a crime than
OL,7,Fmurder and I'm satisfied that his
OL,8,Fprison sentence will likely reflect
OL,9,Fhis having taken someone's life
OL,10,Fdeliberately and without reason."
